{"slug":"sirkuler-24-0295eng","reference":"Sirkuler_24_0295ENG","gazette":"The Official Gazette dated April 5, 2024, and numbered 32511","title":"Changes have been made to the anti-dumping measures on copper pipes originating from Greece.","date":"09 Nisan 2024","bodyHtml":"<p>As a result of the completion of the final review investigation conducted by the Import General Directorate of the Ministry of Trade regarding the import of \"refined copper tubes\" originating from the Hellenic Republic (Greece), the following decisions have been made:</p><p>In the investigated copper tubes, those with non-straight shapes (coil/pancake type) and those with a wall thickness below 0.36 mm are excluded from the scope of the anti-dumping measures (excluded HS codes: 7411.10.90.00.11, 7411.10.90.00.19, and 7411.10.90.00.21).<br></p><p>The anti-dumping measures will continue to be applied as indicated in the following table: they will apply to straight tubes and non-straight tubes with a wall thickness of 0.36 mm or above, but without grooves.&nbsp;</p><p class=\"metin\" style=\"margin:0cm;text-align:justify;text-indent:28.3pt;\r\nline-height:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:9.5pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif;\r\ncolor:black\">&nbsp;</span></p><div align=\"center\">\r\n\r\n<u1:p></u1:p><u1:p></u1:p><table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" width=\"548\" style=\"width:411.1pt;mso-cellspacing:0cm;mso-yfti-tbllook:1184;mso-padding-alt:\r\n 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n <tbody><tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:0;mso-yfti-firstrow:yes;height:1.0pt\">\r\n  <td width=\"21%\" style=\"width:21.0%;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;padding:\r\n  0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:1.0pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:12.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt\">HS Code<u1:p></u1:p></span></b><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"17%\" style=\"width:17.0%;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-left:\r\n  none;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:1.0pt;border-image: initial\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:12.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt\">Description of the Item<u1:p></u1:p></span></b><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"15%\" style=\"width:15.0%;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-left:\r\n  none;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:1.0pt;border-image: initial\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:12.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt\">Country of Origin<u1:p></u1:p></span></b><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"26%\" style=\"text-align: center; width: 26%; border-top: 1pt solid windowtext; border-right: 1pt solid windowtext; border-bottom: 1pt solid windowtext; border-left: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; height: 1pt; border-image: initial;\">\r\n  <span style=\"font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700;\">Company</span></td>\r\n  <td width=\"19%\" style=\"width:19.0%;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-left:\r\n  none;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:1.0pt;border-image: initial\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:12.0pt\"><b><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt\">Anti-Dumping Measure (CIF Percentage of Value)<u1:p></u1:p></span></b><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n </tr>\r\n <tr style=\"mso-yfti-irow:1;height:1.0pt\">\r\n  <td width=\"21%\" style=\"width:21.0%;border:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-top:\r\n  none;padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:1.0pt;border-image: initial\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;line-height:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-size:9.0pt\">7411.10.10.00.00<u1:p></u1:p></span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n  </td>\r\n  <td width=\"17%\" style=\"width:17.0%;border-top:none;border-left:none;\r\n  border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.0pt;border-right:solid windowtext 1.0pt;\r\n  padding:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt;height:1.0pt\">\r\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height:12.0pt